cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper deals with computer vision and graphics, specifically with predicting outdoor illumination from images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves graphics and rendering, which could place it in cs.GR (Computer Graphics). The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves image processing, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia).
